+--------------------+                                +-------------------+
|     Client         |                                |     Server        |
|  (Browser/App)     |                                |   (Node.js API)   |
+--------------------+                                +-------------------+
         |                                                      
         | 1. Login Request: email + password                   
         | -------------------------------------------------->  
         |                                                   
         | 2. Validate credentials                            
         |    - Check user in DB                              
         |    - Compare password                              
         |                                                   
         | 3. Generate JWT (signed with secret key)           
         |    Payload: { userId, email, iat, exp }            
         |                                                   
         | 4. Send back JWT in response                       
         | <-------------------------------------------------- 
         |                                                   
         | 5. Store JWT (localStorage / cookie)               
         |                                                   
         |                                                   
         | 6. Send request to protected route with JWT        
         |    Header: Authorization: Bearer <token>          
         | --------------------------------------------------> 
         |                                                   
         | 7. Server verifies token with secret              
         |    - If valid: grant access                       
         |    - If invalid/expired: reject request           
         |                                                   
         | 8. Send protected resource                        
         | <-------------------------------------------------- 
         |                                                   
